01:24:47,128 --> 01:24:48,546
Sebuah album solo?

1360
01:24:48,588 --> 01:24:49,798
Sebenarnya dua.

1361
01:24:49,839 --> 01:24:51,174
-Berurutan.
-Satu kata lagi...

1362
01:24:51,216 --> 01:24:52,759
