01:27:09,938 --> 01:27:11,106
Halo?

1406
01:27:12,023 --> 01:27:13,942
Paul. Bisa bicara dengan Freddie?

1407
01:27:13,983 --> 01:27:16,486
Mary. Dia tak bisa bicara sekarang.

1408
01:27:16,528 --> 01:27:18,571
Dia bekerja siang malam.

1409
01:27:18,613 --> 01:27:20,198
Tolong kabari dia aku telepon.

1410
01:27:20,240 --> 01:27:22,826
Tenang, Mary, dia di tangan yang tepat.

