Kau bilang kau bermimpi.

1474
01:31:47,882 --> 01:31:49,217
Seperti apa mimpinya?

1475
01:31:50,468 --> 01:31:53,263
Aku coba bicara denganmu, tapi...

1476
01:31:54,222 --> 01:31:56,558
seperti bicara dengan ayahku.

1477
01:31:56,599 --> 01:31:58,893
Kau ingin mengatakan sesuatu...

1478
01:32:00,103 --> 01:32:01,730
tapi tak bisa mengucapkannya.

1479
01:32:03,398 --> 01:32:05,942
Karena kau tak punya suara.

1480
01:32:09,779 --> 01:32:12,282
Freddie, mari sapa tamu baru kita.

1481
01:32:12,991 --> 01:32:14,659
Mereka ingin bertemu denganmu.

1482
01:32:15,910 --> 01:32:17,454
Tunggu sebentar.

1483
01:32:19,122 --> 01:32:20,040
Mary!

1484
01:32:31,092 --> 01:32:33,303
Aku turut bahagia, Mary.

1485
01:32:34,888 --> 01:32:36,431
Sungguh.

1486
01:32:41,269 --> 01:32:42,520
Hanya saja...

1487
01:32:44,856 --> 01:32:46,483
Aku takut.

1488
01:32:46,524 --> 01:32:48,526
Freddie, kau tak perlu takut.

1489
01:32:49,361 --> 01:32:52,072
Karena apa pun yang terjadi, kau dicintai.

1490
01:32:52,614 --> 01:32:55,325
Oleh aku, Brian, Deacy, Roger...

1491
01:32:55,367 --> 01:32:56,826
keluargamu.

1492
01:32:58,661 --> 01:33:00,455
Itu cukup.

1493
01:33:01,581 --> 01:33:03,375
Sementara orang-orang ini...

1494
01:33:04,042 --> 01:33:06,419
mereka tak peduli denganmu.

1495
01:33:07,087 --> 01:33:09,422
Paul tak peduli denganmu.

1496
01:33:10,799 --> 01:33:13,301
Tempatmu bukan di sini, Freddie.

1497
01:33:15,220 --> 01:33:16,680
Pulanglah ke rumah.

1498
01:33:21,184 --> 01:33:22,727
Rumah.

1499
01:33:46,167 --> 01:33:47,544
Freddie!

1500
01:33:51,297 --> 01:33:53,675
Kau sedang apa? Nanti kau kena flu.

1501
01:33:54,801 --> 01:33:57,554
Kenapa kau tak bilang soal Live Aid?

1502
01:33:59,472 --> 01:34:01,641
Pertunjukan amal Afrika?

1503
01:34:02,642 --> 01:34:04,561
Itu memalukan.

1504
01:34:04,602 --> 01:34:06,062
Aku tak mau membuang waktumu.

1505
01:34:10,191 --> 01:34:11,943
Seharusnya kau bilang.

1506
01:34:11,985 --> 01:34:13,319
Aku sudah bilang.

1507
01:34:14,112 --> 01:34:15,405
Kau lupa.

1508
01:34:15,447 --> 01:34:17,240
Kau selalu lupa.

1509
01:34:17,991 --> 01:34:19,659
Masuklah dan minum.

1510
01:34:24,080 --> 01:34:25,248
Keluar.

1511
01:34:26,124 --> 01:34:27,125
Maksudmu?

1512
01:34:29,002 --> 01:34:31,421
Keluarlah dari hidupku.

1513
01:34:34,841 --> 01:34:37,218
Karena hanya aku yang tersisa,
maka kau menyalahkanku?

1514
01:34:38,511 --> 01:34:40,347
Aku menyalahkan diriku.

1515
01:34:41,848 --> 01:34:43,141
Jadi aku keluar?

1516
01:34:43,892 --> 01:34:45,226
Begitu saja?

1517
01:34:46,519 --> 01:34:48,730
Setelah semua yang kita alami?

1518
01:34:50,690 --> 01:34:52,901
Pikirkan foto-foto yang kupunya.

1519
01:34:54,069 --> 01:34:56,738
Aku tahu siapa dirimu, Freddie Mercury.

1520
01:35:00,075 --> 01:35:02,952
Tahu kapan
kau tahu kau sudah membusuk?

1521
01:35:05,372 --> 01:35:06,748
Benar-benar busuk?

1522
01:35:09,084 --> 01:35:10,418
Lalat buah.

1523
01:35:11,586 --> 01:35:14,798
Lalat buah yang kotor.

1524
01:35:15,465 --> 01:35:18,259
Datang untuk memakan sisa-sisa.

1525
01:35:18,301 --> 01:35:21,596
Aku tak meninggalkan banyak sisa
untuk dimakan.

1526
01:35:24,015 --> 01:35:25,058
Jadi, terbanglah pergi.

1527
01:35:25,475 --> 01:35:29,562
Terserah kau mau apa
dengan foto-foto dan ceritamu.

1528
01:35:29,604 --> 01:35:32,273
Tapi berjanjilah satu hal.

1529
01:35:33,566 --> 01:35:35,652
Aku tidak akan melihat wajahmu lagi.

1530
01:35:36,945 --> 01:35:38,154
Selamanya.

1531
01:35:39,489 --> 01:35:40,490
Aku tidak serius.

1532
01:35:43,076 --> 01:35:45,078
Maafkan aku!
Freddie, kembali!

1533
01:35:46,204 --> 01:35:47,831
Aku akan perbaiki.

1534
01:36:03,388 --> 01:36:04,723
Tapi, Peter, mungkin kau benar.

1535
01:36:04,764 --> 01:36:07,434
Aku tidak terluka
dia melepaskanku sebagai teman.

1536
01:36:07,475 --> 01:36:10,061
Tapi kita tak bisa terus
menolong seseorang.

1537
01:36:10,103 --> 01:36:11,646
Jadi, Tn. Prenter...

1538
01:36:11,688 --> 01:36:15,525
cerita-cerita tentang Freddie Mercury
dan para kekasihnya...

1539
01:36:15,567 --> 01:36:17,110
yang begitu banyak.

1540
01:36:17,777 --> 01:36:18,945
Ya?

1541
01:36:18,987 --> 01:36:21,114
-Ini sungguh benar?
-Ya.

1542
01:36:21,156 --> 01:36:22,699
Kekasihnya begitu banyak.

1543
01:36:22,741 --> 01:36:24,367
Tak terhitung.

1544
01:36:25,493 --> 01:36:28,204
Pesta-pesta yang sarat narkoba...

1545
01:36:29,122 --> 01:36:32,292
di situ dia menemukan kekasih baru
setiap malam...

1546
01:36:32,667 --> 01:36:34,919
dan dia tak bisa keluar
dari rutinitas itu.

1547
01:36:34,961 --> 01:36:36,796
Kau melihat siapa dia sebenarnya?

1548
01:36:36,838 --> 01:36:39,466
Aku tahu Freddie
ketika dia membuat Bohemian Rhapsody.

1549
01:36:39,507 --> 01:36:41,092
Dan Freddie yang sekarang...

1550
01:36:42,010 --> 01:36:43,928
dia tidak punya hasrat musik yang sama.

1551
01:36:46,014 --> 01:36:47,140
Halo?

1552
01:36:49,434 --> 01:36:50,268
Halo?

1553
01:36:51,019 --> 01:36:51,853
Miami?

1554
01:36:53,063 --> 01:36:54,230
Freddie?

1555
01:36:54,272 --> 01:36:55,148
Apa kabar?

1556
01:36:55,190 --> 01:36:57,525
Ada konser Afrika...

1557
01:36:57,901 --> 01:36:59,778
yang ingin Queen tampil.

1558
01:36:59,819 --> 01:37:01,363
Itu masih...

1559
01:37:01,404 --> 01:37:02,781
Maksudmu Live Aid?

1560
01:37:02,822 --> 01:37:04,824
Mereka sudah tentukan seluruh band,
Freddie.

1561
01:37:04,866 --> 01:37:06,493
Sudah terlambat.

1562
01:37:07,744 --> 01:37:09,287
Aku ingin...

1563
01:37:09,329 --> 01:37:11,289
Aku ingin bertemu bandku.

1564
01:37:11,998 --> 01:37:14,084
Freddie,
mereka tak mau berurusan denganmu.

1565
01:37:14,125 --> 01:37:16,211
Mereka masih marah.

1566
01:37:17,128 --> 01:37:19,089
Mungkin jika kau yang minta mereka...

1567
01:37:19,130 --> 01:37:20,548
mereka mau menemuiku.

1568
01:37:20,590 --> 01:37:22,467
Bilang aku mau bicara.

1569
01:37:23,259 --> 01:37:24,761
Hanya bicara.

1570
01:37:28,765 --> 01:37:30,392
Kita keluarga.

1571
01:37:33,561 --> 01:37:34,938
Dalam keluarga...

1572
01:37:36,147 --> 01:37:37,732
tentu ada pertengkaran...

1573
01:37:39,693 --> 01:37:41,236
selalu.

1574
01:37:41,861 --> 01:37:43,279
Aku bisa telepon.

1575
01:37:43,947 --> 01:37:45,240
Terima kasih...

1576
01:37:47,200 --> 01:37:48,326
Jim.

1577
01:37:48,368 --> 01:37:50,245
Sebagai teman, seseorang yang...

1578
01:37:50,286 --> 01:37:52,539
mengenal Freddie Mercury
lebih dari orang lain...

1579
01:37:53,123 --> 01:37:56,501
seperti apa sebenarnya dia
sebagai individu?

1580
01:37:57,752 --> 01:37:59,129
Bagiku, Freddie selalu...

1581
01:37:59,713 --> 01:38:02,215
anak Paki yang ketakutan...

1582
01:38:02,257 --> 01:38:04,009
yang takut sendirian.

1583
01:38:04,300 --> 01:38:07,637
Kuharap dia menyadari ini
dan merasa kehilangan dirimu.

1584
01:38:07,679 --> 01:38:09,222
Aku juga berharap begitu.

1585
01:38:09,264 --> 01:38:11,516
Teman yang dekat dan penting.

1586
01:38:27,532 --> 01:38:28,950
Di mana mereka?

1587
01:38:29,701 --> 01:38:31,036
Mereka terlambat.

1588
01:38:38,752 --> 01:38:39,878
Hai, teman-teman.

1589
01:38:39,919 --> 01:38:41,046
Jim.

1590
01:38:43,173 --> 01:38:45,008
Kalau ada yang mau teh, kopi...

1591
01:38:45,050 --> 01:38:46,301
senjata tajam...

1592
01:38:47,719 --> 01:38:49,012
minta saja.

1593
01:38:50,889 --> 01:38:51,890
Jadi...

1594
01:38:53,433 --> 01:38:54,559
siapa yang mau lebih dulu?

1595
01:38:54,601 --> 01:38:55,810
Aku dulu.

1596
01:38:57,687 --> 01:38:59,314
Sikapku buruk.

1597
01:38:59,356 --> 01:39:01,024
Aku tahu itu, dan...

1598
01:39:01,524 --> 01:39:02,817
aku pantas dicaci maki.

1599
01:39:03,943 --> 01:39:05,153
Aku sombong...

1600
01:39:06,821 --> 01:39:08,281
egois.

1601
01:39:11,868 --> 01:39:13,787
Intinya aku menyebalkan.

1602
01:39:13,828 --> 01:39:15,038
Awal yang bagus.

1603
01:39:16,706 --> 01:39:18,667
Aku mau saja membuka bajuku...

1604
01:39:18,708 --> 01:39:20,835
dan mencambuk diriku di depan kalian.

1605
01:39:23,838 --> 01:39:26,091
Atau aku bisa beri pertanyaan sederhana.

1606
01:39:26,132 --> 01:39:27,300
Aku pilih cambuk.

1607
01:39:32,305 --> 01:39:34,641
Apa yang harus kulakukan
agar kalian memaafkanku?

1608
01:39:35,016 --> 01:39:36,893
Itu maumu, Freddie?

1609
01:39:38,311 --> 01:39:39,396
Aku memaafkanmu.

1610
01:39:39,437 --> 01:39:41,064
-Itu saja? Boleh kami pergi?
-Tidak.

1611
01:39:47,278 --> 01:39:48,863
Aku pergi ke Munich.

1612
01:39:48,905 --> 01:39:50,740
Aku mengupah banyak orang.

1613
01:39:50,782 --> 01:39:52,826
Aku mengatur mereka...

1614
01:39:52,867 --> 01:39:54,160
dan masalahnya...

1615
01:39:57,205 --> 01:39:58,248
mereka menurut.

1616
01:40:00,208 --> 01:40:02,419
Tidak ada perdebatan dari Roger.

1617
01:40:04,045 --> 01:40:05,630
Tidak ada penulisan ulang darimu.

1618
01:40:06,506 --> 01:40:08,091
Tidak ada wajah lucunya.

1619
01:40:12,762 --> 01:40:14,139
Aku butuh kalian.

1620
01:40:17,892 --> 01:40:19,394
Dan kalian butuh aku.

1621
01:40:24,441 --> 01:40:26,818
Hadapi saja.
Kita lumayan untuk empat ratu tua.

1622
01:40:29,362 --> 01:40:30,905
Jadi, silakan.

1623
01:40:31,406 --> 01:40:33,116
Sebut persyaratan kalian.

1624
01:40:34,909 --> 01:40:36,995
Bisa beri kami waktu, Fred?

1625
01:40:53,511 --> 01:40:54,929
Kenapa kau lakukan itu?

1626
01:40:54,971 --> 01:40:56,222
Karena ingin saja.

1627
01:41:09,194 --> 01:41:11,654
Mereka akan tenang.
Hanya butuh sedikit waktu.

1628
01:41:13,656 --> 01:41:15,450
Jika aku tak punya waktu?

1629
01:41:17,994 --> 01:41:19,746
Apa maksudmu, Fred?

1630
01:41:25,752 --> 01:41:27,712
Kau boleh masuk kembali kalau mau.

1631
01:41:33,885 --> 01:41:34,886
Kami memutuskan...

1632
01:41:36,388 --> 01:41:37,305
Apa keputusan kita?

1633
01:41:38,056 --> 01:41:39,224
Mulai sekarang...

1634
01:41:39,265 --> 01:41:42,560
setiap lagu, siapa pun penulisnya,
musik, lirik...

1635
01:41:42,936 --> 01:41:44,187
itu adalah karya Queen.

1636
01:41:44,562 --> 01:41:46,898
Bukan satu dari kita, hanya Queen.

1637
01:41:46,940 --> 01:41:50,610
Semua penghasilan, semua pujian,
dibagi empat secara rata.

1638
01:41:50,944 --> 01:41:51,778
Baik.

1639
01:41:52,237 --> 01:41:54,197
Kami ada masalah
dengan orang-orang di sekitarmu.

1640
01:41:54,239 --> 01:41:55,699
Paul sudah kupecat.

1641
01:41:55,740 --> 01:41:57,867
-Atas alasan apa?
-Dia jahat.

1642
01:41:57,909 --> 01:41:58,785
Apa lagi?

1643
01:41:59,285 --> 01:42:00,453
Bob Geldof.

1644
01:42:00,495 --> 01:42:04,457
Kubujuk dia agar kalian bisa masuk
konser Live Aid...

1645
01:42:04,499 --> 01:42:06,167
tapi dia minta jawaban sekarang.

1646
01:42:06,459 --> 01:42:08,336
Kalian harus buat keputusan.

1647
01:42:09,879 --> 01:42:11,548
Karcis terjual habis.

1648
01:42:11,589 --> 01:42:13,425
100.000 orang di Wembley...

1649
01:42:13,466 --> 01:42:16,720
100.000 orang di Stadion JFK
di Philadelphia...

1650
01:42:16,761 --> 01:42:20,265
penonton di 150 negara...

1651
01:42:20,306 --> 01:42:21,683
13 satelit.

1652
01:42:22,100 --> 01:42:24,352
Olimpiade hanya dapat tiga.

1653
01:42:25,270 --> 01:42:27,272
Sudah lama kita tidak main musik bersama.

1654
01:42:27,313 --> 01:42:28,898
Bunuh diri bermain lagi...

1655
01:42:28,940 --> 01:42:30,734
untuk pertama kali
di depan jutaan orang.

1656
01:42:30,775 --> 01:42:33,528
Tepatnya 1,5 miliar.

1657
01:42:35,155 --> 01:42:36,948
"Siapa empat dinosaurus ini?"

1658
01:42:37,365 --> 01:42:38,950
"Di mana Madonna?"

1659
01:42:38,992 --> 01:42:41,244
Berdurasi 20 menit. Semua dapat sama.

1660
01:42:41,870 --> 01:42:43,872
Jagger, Bowie...

1661
01:42:44,706 --> 01:42:45,832
Elton...

1662
01:42:46,291 --> 01:42:49,044
McCartney, The Who...

1663
01:42:49,085 --> 01:42:50,712
Led Zeppelin...

1664
01:42:50,754 --> 01:42:53,381
Phil Collins, REO Speedwagon...

1665
01:42:54,299 --> 01:42:55,800
Bob Dylan.

1666
01:42:55,842 --> 01:42:57,093
Mereka bintang besar.

1667
01:42:57,135 --> 01:42:59,095
Semua orang terkenal ikut konser ini.

1668
01:42:59,137 --> 01:42:59,929
Dengar.

1669
01:43:00,472 --> 01:43:01,681
Yang kutahu...

1670
01:43:02,098 --> 01:43:05,769
jika kita bangun sehari
setelah konser ini...

1671
01:43:06,519 --> 01:43:08,688
dan kita tidak terlibat...

1672
01:43:10,231 --> 01:43:12,942
kita akan menyesal sampai mati.

1673
01:43:20,033 --> 01:43:21,326
Kumohon.

1674
01:43:28,625 --> 01:43:32,337
Di San Francisco setiap hari
dua orang menerima kabar buruk...

1675
01:43:32,379 --> 01:43:34,172
"Kau mengidap AIDS, tak ada obatnya."

1676
01:43:34,214 --> 01:43:38,093
Sejak para dokter di Prancis dan Amerika
mengisolasi virusnya tahun 1983...

1677
01:43:38,134 --> 01:43:40,720
penelitian berjalan begitu cepat.

1678
01:43:40,762 --> 01:43:44,265
Metode yang digunakan virus
untuk merusak sistem kekebalan tubuh...

1679
01:43:44,307 --> 01:43:45,725
telah ditemukan...

1680
01:43:45,767 --> 01:43:48,395
namun entah kapan obatnya ditemukan.

1681
01:43:48,978 --> 01:43:51,356
Terobosan besarnya adalah
tes darah baru...

1682
01:43:51,398 --> 01:43:52,982
yang menjamin di masa mendatang...

1683
01:43:53,024 --> 01:43:55,902
tak ada yang menulari AIDS
lewat transfusi darah.

1684
01:43:55,944 --> 01:43:58,071
Tapi penggunaannya baru disetujui.

1685
01:43:58,113 --> 01:44:03,827
What is this thing that builds our dreams

1686
01:44:03,868 --> 01:44:09,666
Yet slips away from us?

1687
01:44:11,501 --> 01:44:17,465
Who wants to live forever?

1688
01:44:18,008 --> 01:44:24,347
Who wants to live forever?

1689
01:44:31,396 --> 01:44:35,358
There's no chance for us

1690
01:44:37,402 --> 01:44:42,073
It's all decided for us

1691
01:44:44,034 --> 01:44:48,955
This world has only one

1692
01:44:48,997 --> 01:44:54,502
Sweet moment set aside for us

1693
01:44:58,089 --> 01:44:59,591
Kau mengerti?

1694
01:45:01,176 --> 01:45:06,473
Kita bisa melakukan beberapa perawatan
yang tersedia.

1695
01:45:06,514 --> 01:45:09,184
Perawatannya tidak terlalu efektif,
Freddie.

1696
01:46:21,840 --> 01:46:22,841
Ya.

1697
01:46:24,843 --> 01:46:26,094
-Sudah dulu.
-Baik.

1698
01:46:27,178 --> 01:46:28,221
Maaf.

1699
01:46:29,097 --> 01:46:30,098
Suaraku jelek.

1700
01:46:31,725 --> 01:46:34,102
Suara kalian sangat bagus.

1701
01:46:34,894 --> 01:46:35,895
Sudah lama.

1702
01:46:36,604 --> 01:46:38,648
Kerongkonganku terasa tidak enak.

1703
01:46:39,274 --> 01:46:40,734
Masih ada satu pekan.

1704
01:46:40,775 --> 01:46:41,901
Kita pasti bisa.

1705
01:46:41,943 --> 01:46:43,820
Semua berjalan baik, Fred.

1706
01:46:43,862 --> 01:46:45,697
Hanya butuh istirahat saja.

1707
01:46:46,906 --> 01:46:47,907
Ya.

1708
01:46:48,575 --> 01:46:49,826
Mau minum, Rog?

1709
01:46:49,868 --> 01:46:51,745
Ya, ada bar tak jauh dari sini.

1710
01:46:51,786 --> 01:46:52,912
Boleh aku ikut?

1711
01:46:52,954 --> 01:46:54,664
-Kami tidak...
-Tentu tidak.

1712
01:46:54,706 --> 01:46:56,833
-Khusus undangan.
-Kau baik sekali.

1713
01:46:56,875 --> 01:46:58,335
Sebelum kalian pergi...

1714
01:47:00,628 --> 01:47:02,172
bisa bicara sebentar?

1715
01:47:02,714 --> 01:47:04,507
Ya. Ada apa?

1716
01:47:07,552 --> 01:47:08,970
